> Maxima raced away from the very place she was just taken to.

inferior 
> with out her amazing abilities to detect things from long

>

>

jet

>

form. 
> 
> Soon enough, she reached the wreckage. Amazing enough, it didn't 
seem 
> that any one had noticed her arrival other than Wheeljack, Ragnar,

> "Wheeljack?" She padded inside the wreck. "Wheekjack?!"

"Over here!" he calls from under a console.  Only his legs are 
visible.  "I've met a lot of pretty girls in my lifetime, but this is 
the first time one's come looking for me.  What's up?"
